{
  "texts": [
    "Each of these domains are considered individually from the viewpoint of how AI may automate and augment it.",
    "SLPs routinely collaborate with professionals such as educators, physicians, and psychologists to deliver coordinated care.",
    "AI will be an additional entity to collaborate with (Duvenaud, 2025) as a tool that can enhance efficiency and streamline communication.",
    "For example, AI-powered EHRs can aggregate interdisciplinary notes, highlight inconsistencies, and suggest care pathways.",
    "Such systems may reduce administrative burden, operational delays, and documentation errors, improving continuity of care."
  ]
}